dc_title_s: Mexico--east coast, Gulf of Mexico, Isla de Piedras to Progreso (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by spot heights. "From Mexican charts and commercial surveys to 1985." Not distributed to depository libraries. "Soundings in meters." "Copyright 1998 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." Includes source diagram. Map No.28220 This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
